For sale by Public Tender closing on Thursday 27th August 2009 at 9.30am. EST

CBRE is proud to offer for sale this office suite investment located in Liverpool. The property benefits from a prominent position in a strong commercial area.

Property highlights include:

- Net income: $49,000* pa
- New 3 year lease with 2 x 3 year options
- Annual CPI increases
- Leased to Sydney Ultrasound for Woman
- Central Liverpool location close to transport

The property will be auctioned on Tuesday, 17 November, 2015 unless sold prior.

This property represents an excellent opportunity to secure a strong performing commercial office suite investment in a sought-after location, rarely offered to the open market.

CBRE, on behalf of BreakThru, are pleased to offer Suite 107, 161 Bigge Street, Liverpool for sale.

The suite boasts the following attributes:

• Medical suite in the heart of Liverpool CBD
• 104sqm* internal + 1 parking space
• Potential for an investor or owner occupier
• Annual income of $33,119.52 + GST NET
• Currently leased until 29/10/2016
• Walking distance to Liverpool Westfield & Train Station
• Situated behind Liverpool's future 'Elizabeth Street' development project
• Well positioned to take advantage of future residential developments in Liverpool CBD

The property will be sold by Public Auction on Tuesday, 19th April 2016 as part of an Auction Portfolio at 10:30AM.

The Auction will be held at Auctionworks, Mezzanine Level, 50 Margaret Street, Sydney.

To obtain further information, please contact the listed agents.

CBRE is pleased to present 51 Goulburn Street, Liverpool to market for sale via Public Auction, under instructions from Receivers and Managers, Jennifer Nettleton and Cassandra Mathews of KordaMentha. 

The site represents a quality investment and future development opportunity (STCA) in a prime location in the heart of Liverpool's medical precinct. Boasting a generous site area of 962 square metres* and FSR of 2.5:1, the site offers a multitude of potential uses under the dynamic B4 – mixed use zoning (STCA). 

51 Goulburn Street offers the following key attributes:
- Currently returning $150,000 gross p.a.
- 5+5 year lease to South West Radiology 
- Site area: 962 square metres*
- Flexible B4 – Mixed Use zoning
- FSR: 2.5:1 
- Proximity to Liverpool Hospital and moments from Liverpool Train Station & Westfield 

For further information about the property, please contact the CBRE team.
